{"tid":1637184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實民陣點解唔搞返次撐警遊行？","createTime":"2019-10-08T02:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:29:18.000Z","uid":172506,"like":51,"dislike":276,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"3414b655023d5b6a5478173f41036d396e715e94","tid":1637184,"uid":172506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:06:29.000Z","msg":"雖然有啲老調重彈<br />\n但係都可以運用佢地嘅影響力向世人明確表示而家popo同港共醜陋嘅一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持警察嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n無錯！重點係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嚴正執法</span></span></strong><br />\n嚴格、正當咁執行法律<br />\n要求popo遵守返警察通例<br />\n特別係展示返委任證/編號、配合現場記者採訪工作，重點係各種使用武力嘅準則<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">支持基本法、落實一國兩制、（反港獨）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n要求港府遵守基本法規定<br />\n落實高度自治（中央政府不得干預香港內政）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">保民生、護法治、捍經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n指出現時亂局由政府無法處理「暴徒」行為<br />\n影響到經濟<br />\n要求林鄭月娥盡快回應港人訴求以平息「動亂」<br />\n守護香港經濟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然藍媒咁鍾意做標題黨<br />\n如果popo仍然唔肯批不反對通知書<br />\n我都想睇下港共同班仆街點兜<br />\n雖然未必有好大效用<br />\n但既然都無嘢輸 預咗佢唔批 何樂而不為？<br />\n（批咗 自己人見到民陣搞應該都會get到照出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"ed03ec18ad7795a3a923fea752d733773feb4568","tid":1637184,"uid":172506,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:07:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br 